{% comment %}
============================================================
セクション名: ブランドストーリー
用途: 代表者の想いや創業背景を伝え、ブランドへの共感と信頼を獲得するためのセクション
推奨設置場所: トップページの中盤・About ページ・LP のストーリー紹介箇所
カスタマイズポイント:
  - 代表者の写真(肖像画像)
  - ラベル(「Brand Story」などの英字キャッチ)
  - 見出し・本文(創業背景・想いを記述)
  - 代表者の名前・肩書き(署名)
  - 引用文(印象的なメッセージを強調表示)
  - 詳しく見るボタン(リンク先・文字)
  - 背景色・文字色・画像配置(左右切り替え)
注意点:
  - 代表者写真は縦長または正方形(推奨 800 × 1000px、JPEG または PNG)を用意する
  - 本文はリッチテキストなので改行・太字・リンクが使える
  - モバイルでは画像が上、テキストが下に自動配置される
動作確認バージョン: Online Store 2.0
ライセンス: ALSEL Original
============================================================
{% endcomment %}

<section class="alsel-brand-story alsel-brand-story--{{ section.settings.image_position }}" aria-label="{{ section.settings.heading | escape }}">
  <div class="alsel-brand-story__inner">
    <div class="alsel-brand-story__media">
      {%- if section.settings.portrait != blank -%}
        {%- assign alt_1 = section.settings.author_name | escape -%}
{{ section.settings.portrait
          | image_url: width: 800
          | image_tag: loading: 'lazy', class: 'alsel-brand-story__image', alt: alt_1, widths: '375, 600, 800, 1000', sizes: '(min-width: 750px) 45vw, 100vw' }}
      {%- else -%}
        <div class="alsel-brand-story__placeholder" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      {%- endif -%}
    </div>

    <div class="alsel-brand-story__content">
      {%- if section.settings.label != blank -%}
        <span class="alsel-brand-story__label">{{ section.settings.label | escape }}</span>
      {%- endif -%}

      {%- if section.settings.heading != blank -%}
        <h2 class="alsel-brand-story__heading">{{ section.settings.heading }}</h2>
      {%- endif -%}

      {%- if section.settings.quote != blank -%}
        <blockquote class="alsel-brand-story__quote">
          {{ section.settings.quote }}
        </blockquote>
      {%- endif -%}

      {%- if section.settings.body != blank -%}
        <div class="alsel-brand-story__body">{{ section.settings.body }}</div>
      {%- endif -%}

      {%- if section.settings.author_name != blank or section.settings.author_role != blank -%}
        <div class="alsel-brand-story__signature">
          {%- if section.settings.author_role != blank -%}
            <span class="alsel-brand-story__role">{{ section.settings.author_role | escape }}</span>
          {%- endif -%}
          {%- if section.settings.author_name != blank -%}
            <span class="alsel-brand-story__name">{{ section.settings.author_name | escape }}</span>
          {%- endif -%}
        </div>
      {%- endif -%}

      {%- if section.settings.cta_text != blank and section.settings.cta_link != blank -%}
        <a class="alsel-brand-story__cta" href="{{ section.settings.cta_link }}" aria-label="{{ section.settings.cta_text | escape }}">
          {{ section.settings.cta_text | escape }}
          <span class="alsel-brand-story__arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
      {%- endif -%}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .alsel-brand-story {
    --story-bg: {{ section.settings.bg_color }};
    --story-text: {{ section.settings.text_color }};
    --story-accent: {{ section.settings.accent_color }};
    --story-cta-bg: {{ section.settings.cta_bg }};
    --story-cta-color: {{ section.settings.cta_color }};
    background: var(--story-bg);
    color: var(--story-text);
    padding: 3rem 1.25rem;
  }
  .alsel-brand-story__inner {
    max-width: 1180px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .alsel-brand-story__media { width: 100%; }
  .alsel-brand-story__image {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    border-radius: 8px;
    object-fit: cover;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
  }
  .alsel-brand-story__placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e5e7eb, #cbd5e1);
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  .alsel-brand-story__content { line-height: 1.8; }
  .alsel-brand-story__label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--story-accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .alsel-brand-story__heading {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4.5vw, 2.4rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.4;
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
  }
  .alsel-brand-story__quote {
    border-left: 3px solid var(--story-accent);
    padding: 0.25rem 0 0.25rem 1rem;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-style: normal;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .alsel-brand-story__body { font-size: 0.98rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .alsel-brand-story__body p { margin: 0 0 1rem; }
  .alsel-brand-story__signature {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
    padding-top: 1rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }
  .alsel-brand-story__role { font-size: 0.85rem; opacity: 0.75; }
  .alsel-brand-story__name { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; }
  .alsel-brand-story__cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.85rem 1.75rem;
    background: var(--story-cta-bg);
    color: var(--story-cta-color);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
  }
  .alsel-brand-story__cta:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
  }
  .alsel-brand-story__arrow { transition: transform 0.2s ease; }
  .alsel-brand-story__cta:hover .alsel-brand-story__arrow { transform: translateX(4px); }

  @media (min-width: 750px) {
    .alsel-brand-story { padding: 5rem 2rem; }
    .alsel-brand-story__inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 4rem;
    }
    .alsel-brand-story--right .alsel-brand-story__media { order: 2; }
    .alsel-brand-story--right .alsel-brand-story__content { order: 1; }
  }
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "ブランドストーリー",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "alsel-section",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "メイン設定"
